com.interpss.core.aclf.hvdc

Interface HvdcLine2TCCC

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Branch, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, HvdcLine2T, IAclfAdjustment, IAdaptable, IBranchSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HvdcLine2TCCCImpl

    public interface HvdcLine2TCCC
extends HvdcLine2T
    A representation of the model object 'Line2 T'. Always assume fromBus(rectifier) -> toBus(invetor)

    The following features are supported:

    • Line R
    • Compond R
    • Control Mode
    • Operation Mode
    • Meter End
    • Control Side
    • Power Demand
    • Power Demand2
    • Scheduled DC Voltage
    • Rectifier
    • Inverter
    • Rectifier2
    • Inverter2
    See Also:
    HvdcLinePackage.getHvdcLine2TCCC()
